\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我轉咗食英美澳加豬好耐....價錢差不多又好食啲。"},{"pid":"33e8108936cdaad6d8d6d356edd91daa8d19df37","tid":1512391,"uid":31510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c93e3965e26c9149d241e1dc1b41dc12268e157","tid":1512391,"uid":225898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9d47f2d215d8261faa0b7d724511c946d9c18f","tid":1512391,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />豬都食豬"},{"pid":"05cc6a93dca0c1580dbdc91bb5797df88a53f5f5","tid":1512391,"uid":288610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:22:01.000Z","msg":"大6豬同豬交配咪解決供應問題囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0461c7c492cdf0fcb378664eee654b40dcf297","tid":1512391,"uid":65074,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:24:52.000Z","msg":"我就唔食大陸豬啦<br />\n留返俾大陸人食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我建議中國這樣懲罰香港：<br />\n1. 不准香港加入大灣區，等香港沒得分享當大灣區人的榮耀<br />\n2. 不准香港建三跑，人工島，使香港少了未來發展方向<br />\n3. 停止每日 150 殖民，令香港人口老化<br />\n3.5 與中國人通婚之港人，其香港藉改為中國藉，需申請簽證才可去香港，吸走香港的勞動力<br />\n4. 停東江水，令香港被迫另求水源建海水化淡廠<br />\n5. 撤走駐港解放軍，使美軍攻擊香港時的沒人保衛香港<br />\n6. 要求所有中國教職員和優才辭職，返中國工作，貢獻自己才能知識、唔益香港人，你以為搞科研就請回香港人<br />\n7. 將工聯會撤回中國，香港不配有那麼好的工會，等你班人無得學中國象棋<br />\n8. 在香港買奶粉回國，一律無期徙刑，等你香港人無得賺奶粉錢<br />\n9. 不再委任特首，等你自己選，以後特首級人才留給你慢慢用<br />\n10. 不教普通話與簡體字，香港人永遠學不會講不好中國的文明語言與規範文字，被中國人當醜小鴨排斥<br />\n11.強制所有中國國民即日撤走香港所有資產，規定包括不可持有任何香港物業、不可擔任公司股東、不可持有任何香港銀行之戶口、不可進行任何融資，違反者將會&rsquo;立即送中&rsquo;，回國後即判無期徙刑<br />\n<br />\n既然上面的東西全部益你，快些拿走，等班香港人哭住要認錯。"},{"pid":"bd39fa405a1a73336b742582b573e6ab0b2a7257","tid":1512391,"uid":95445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:37:09.000Z","msg":"大陸豬搶豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6612ba96f0479713af30a0c130afe00766560d55","tid":1512391,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5505abff863b41ab8e6c4799d3d09c7288d12f71","tid":1512391,"uid":96472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:40:25.000Z","msg":"暴徒搗亂超市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ff733f6f8c1aef57448ec27b44409c0115b80e","tid":1512391,"uid":147880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe718d4e2a2b418ce626168a64104a5ef1efbdc","tid":1512391,"uid":276484,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6bc2a8189aff840706c5c7887b130672c0da0b11","tid":1512391,"uid":125079,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9b7e1eea72925a462933d506ba0eb10f9e1aaa3d","tid":1512391,"uid