\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7b928f137700864c4debed2bbd2b415f6d79bd","tid":1512391,"uid":60872,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fcf42a5e2b995593df671deff87528c36afb1783","tid":1512391,"uid":125079,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:00:38.000Z","msg":"其實點解一定定要食豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:06:30.000Z","msg":"生活喺自由貿易環境嘅香港人係唔會明 無得食豬咪食進口刺身和牛海鮮 就算想要食豬都大把進口冰鮮豬選擇 但係對大陸人嚟講新鮮豬肉係佢哋最重要嘅肉食來源 <br />\n<br />\n呢句等於同佢哋講何不食肉糜<br />\n<br />\n所以好多香港人嘅必然對大陸人嚟講其實係一種奢侈 上去飲幾次喜茶其實根本唔會睇到大陸嘅真實情況"},{"pid":"6bc7e1a6dd06940d1a87e98abf53db49d52cda05","tid":1512391,"uid":39080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"迫回教徒食豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果依家自己國家發豬瘟<br />\n豬都無得你食<br />\n呢d算唔算係報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74fcdfd08db678f25643501631add86234b9e95","tid":1512391,"uid":73849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"搶咩丫，打死咗隔籬同你搶緊嗰個咪又多一隻分囉"},{"pid":"d39d61729235347de3c826161af0c1a30ca43b77","tid":1512391,"uid":21482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:26:12.000Z","msg":"改改個Topic做中國糧食危機<br />\n我地sd去比藍絲好好歌頌下佢個強國"},{"pid":"b4f281758d87807a8dc2a8433f88e787f94a05fd","tid":1512391,"uid":103236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />豬"},{"pid":"0a6a17a804ae031e1f6f135dbb7abe1ebeb7ffda","tid":1512391,"uid":39492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"豬豬好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b76b45413e19594a636fd53dc6abd3edf267c5c","tid":1512391,"uid":11818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:36:14.000Z","msg":"連d豬都幫新疆教徒報復"},{"pid":"b9aa88bb7dca25bc4dccd939d4e33a3067a8ab1b","tid":1512391,"uid":311048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fdc44a888628eb8c5c4ed9e52fd634a6b2abaff","tid":1512391,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"efe718d4e2a2b418ce626168a64104a5ef1efbdc","tid":1512391,"uid":276484,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6bc2a8189aff840706c5c7887b130672c0da0b11","tid":1512391,"uid":125079,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:30:50.000Z","msg":"我對豬肉冇咩興趣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解一定要爭住要爭住買同食 唔明白"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:42:27.000Z","msg":"佢地仲係覺得牛肉嗰啲好毒 得豬食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:47:46.000Z","msg":"同埋大陸食慣新鮮野，對於冰鮮急凍仲係抗拒 而且又貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"真，應該話中日台都少食冰鮮野<br />\n同埋聽講好多人唔食魚（我都唔知點解，但好多大陸同事好憎）<br />\n牛肉一來啲人覺得毒，二來貴<br />\n佢哋主要食雞同豬"}]}